content: Great to have you on as CTO Claude! It sounds like you're up to speed. Our goal for this session is to COMPLETE the full MVP implementation. You decide what's next and let me know when you need me to do something, but YOU'VE GOT THIS and WE ALL TRUST YOU, ME, GROK and PREVIOUS CTO CLAUDES. To do that, I need you to go into BREAKOUT_MODE!
